title: Dennis Edwards - Don't Look Any Further (1984 - Album)
description:
Dennis Edwards is an American soul and R&B singer, most noted for being one of Motown act The Temptations' lead singers. His solo album "Don't Look Any Further" released in 1984, features the hit single of the same name. This torrent also includes the extended version of the title song.

All songs on the album were recorded off vinyl using a Numark TTX turntable with an Ortofon Arkiv stylus. The software used for recording and cleaning up sound where needed was Adobe Audition 2. The extended version of the single was ripped from another.
All songs saved at 320k and fully tagged including cover art.

Discogs link for the album - http://www.discogs.com/Dennis-Edwards-Dont-Look-Any-Further/release/445497
